Mission Orders

The pirates down by the dock are plotting against the federation.

Kill the {@LinkCreature:11#2003#Red Lash sentinels}, {@LinkCreature:11#1008#pirates}, {@LinkCreature:11#2001#mates}, {@LinkCreature:11#1003#veterans}, and {@LinkCreature:11#3006#berserkers}.

Report to a guild quest reward coordinator when mission is complete.
